Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I can't make it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could Hattori and\NKazuha have gone there?
