Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can ask for directions at a police box to help us find the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A couple of high school kids that speak in Kansai accent?
