Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lawyer's lapel pin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but aren't you\NMiss Misari Ito, a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No joke
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am, but.
