Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you happen to know a suspicious\NItou residence around here?
