Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say that there's a building that bears a nameplate Itou,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:12:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,right behind the elementary school on 5th street where,
