Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brat tried to shout and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caught him in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hell! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You surprise me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an acquaintance of the Kogoro Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really know a lot of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,high school kid detective,\NMr. Heiji Hattori, don't you?
