Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how to evade taxes illegally.\NHe had the tape to prove my doings
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but didn't want to publicize it.
