Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, that's all he could tell us before he stopped breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's when we got a call from this boy.
