Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it a second thought and could you tell me once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who the stinking rat really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get funny, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So you haven't learned your lesson well enough.
