Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What bothers you, dear little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The footprints-of shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there are many wet shoe marks,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I was wondering where all those people are in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
