Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThey are my footprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They stuck a gun at me in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got handcuffed, then brought straight into this attic and was confined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the footprint of my sneakers for jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're yours?
