Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about me, feel free to come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:17:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
