Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ARAB. Swab)\NNow, leading by three to four lengths!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,44A»\\NGood, keep on leading to the finish, hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look we have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but to break this glass and make them notice us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do, you brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They scared me stiff alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, guys, time for your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better make the most of your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the famous high school detective in Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help Hattori, it should come easier to you than your math, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a simple cipher to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get to your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And be sure to solve it by sundown,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you don't want end up like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to stay on this side of the world, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take time, relax and solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is there anything to worry about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told us that the same cipher will be delivered
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to his detective agency tomorrow by the delivery service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He attached a letter that says that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:20:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the cipher is for a seven digit ID number to the Toto Bank safe-deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He assumed he was safe because of that arrangement and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was arrogant enough to tell me that he wouldn't say anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if I stop giving instructions on illegal tax evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he was going to blackmail me and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,use the money for gambling that he loved so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I remember Dad told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kusukawa is known for loving to gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a little more time and leave me alone,I think I can solve it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll have tea downstairs and will wait for you while you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,make full use of your brain to solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't even think of running away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:20:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for us without expecting anything from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's alright now Mr. Kusukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still alive right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dust around your nose was moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the son of the Chief for you.,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really unconscious a\NIittle while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just play dead for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they find out you're alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,their going to threat us to solve the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The answer to this puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer?\NYou found out the answer to the puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you liek gambling this puzzle is easy to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Mr. Kusukawa, is the puzzle paper only this one copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, unless they made a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great to hear, when I'm about to gamble something really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numbers and 4 letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Q AK.)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, did you find out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dice steak?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hinomaru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.31,0:24:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the middle is the letter "Q"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji Hattori - No Way Out\NPart 2
